00:18:20.020 --> 00:18:22.020
Not that I know of.

00:18:22.219 --> 00:18:24.219
Not that I know of.

00:18:24.219 --> 00:18:27.219
It's used in plenty of businesses in commercial context.

00:18:27.219 --> 00:18:31.219
