00:18:31.219 --> 00:18:33.219
Any plans for Keras 4

00:18:36.219 --> 00:18:39.219
that didn't get implemented in Keras 3?

00:18:40.219 --> 00:18:42.219
No.

00:18:42.219 --> 00:18:44.219
Not yet.

00:18:44.219 --> 00:18:46.219
Keras 3 is out and you take a breath.

00:18:46.219 --> 00:18:48.219
Appreciate it.

